---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - DailySpark">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6">Last Updated: January 29, 2025</p>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">When you visit DailySpark, we may collect:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
        <li>Information you provide directly (such as when contacting us via email)</li>
        <li>Automatically collected information (IP addresses, browser type, device information)</li>
        <li>Cookies and similar tracking technologies</li>
        <li>Analytics data about how you use our website</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">We use collected information to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
        <li>Provide and improve our content and services</li>
        <li>Respond to your inquiries and communications</li>
        <li>Track affiliate conversions through our partner AWIN</li>
        <li>Analyze website usage to improve user experience</li>
        <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">3. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">We work with third-party services including:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
        <li><strong>AWIN:</strong> Our affiliate marketing partner who tracks conversions when you click affiliate links</li>
        <li><strong>MyPhysicianPlan:</strong> The healthcare service we recommend, who has their own privacy policy</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics Providers:</strong> To understand website usage patterns</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-4">These partners may collect information directly from you through cookies and tracking pixels.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">4. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">We use cookies to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
        <li>Remember your preferences</li>
        <li>Track affiliate referrals (30-day cookie duration via AWIN)</li>
        <li>Analyze website traffic and usage</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-4">You can control cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may affect site functionality and affiliate tracking.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">5. Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Depending on your location, you may have rights including:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
        <li>Access to your personal information</li>
        <li>Correction of inaccurate data</li>
        <li>Deletion of your information</li>
        <li>Opt-out of marketing communications</li>
        <li>Data portability</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">6. California Privacy Rights (CCPA)</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">California residents have additional rights under the CCPA, including the right to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
        <li>Know what personal information is collected</li>
        <li>Request deletion of personal information</li>
        <li>Opt-out of the sale of personal information</li>
        <li>Non-discrimination for exercising privacy rights</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">7. GDPR Compliance (EU Residents)</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">For EU residents, we comply with GDPR requirements including:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
        <li>Lawful basis for processing (consent or legitimate interest)</li>
        <li>Right to erasure ("right to be forgotten")</li>
        <li>Data portability rights</li>
        <li>Right to object to processing</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">8. Data Security</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">9. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Our website is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children under 13.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">10. Contact Information</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">For privacy-related inquiries or to exercise your rights, contact us at:</p>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Email: brice@dailyspark.com<br>
        Company: DailySpark<br>
        Operated by: Jax Sod Inc.<br>
        Location: Jacksonville, Florida
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The updated version will be indicated by an updated "Last Updated" date.</p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>